{"id":"428835640537739_505977066156929","type":"status","created_time":"2013-07-15T16:11:08+0000","message":"Strong Condemnation and protest against killing of 4 Jamaat-Shibir men in Kustia and Chanpainababgonj:\n\nGovt. must pay its due if it doesn\u2019t punish the killers- Shibir\n\nBangladesh Islami Chhatrashibir strongly slammed and protested against killing of two Shibir men at Mirpur in Kustia and another two in Chanpainababgonj during the shutdown today.\n\nIn a protest statement, the Secretary-General of Bangladesh Islami Chhatrashibir Abdul Jabbar said, \u201cThe Awami fascist government has, on one hand, planned to kill national leaders through a farcical tribunal and, on the other hand, also strewed Awami goons to kill Shibir men. The Awami terrorists killed two meritorious students named Al-Mukid Tarun, an HSC 2nd year student, and Sabuj Ahmed, a class ten student, with rod, batons and sharp weapons in broad daylight. Besides, A Jamaat activist named Nurul Islam and an HSC 2nd year Shibir activist named Ziaur Rahman has been killed as a result of wanton fire of the police and BGB at Shibgonj in Chanpainababgonj during the hartal today. Another named Saddam Hussen injured in Kustia is in critical condition now.\u201d\n\nHe urged the government to bring the killers to book, provide damages and, furthermore, refrain from such heinous jobs in the coming days."}